<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">——区块链学生校内实训项目体验</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;">一、寻求实践之路的初衷 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;">作为一名区块链技术专业的学生，我深知理论知识与实际工作之间的鸿沟。为了弥补这一差距，我开始寻找将所学知识应用到实际项目中的机会，渴望在实践中深化对知识的理解，提升自己的专业技能。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;">二、区块链项目的探索之旅 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;">在“先锋积分系统”项目中，我经历了从理论到实践的转变。通过项目需求分析、设计、开发和测试等各个环节，我不仅深入了解了区块链技术的核心原理，还学会了如何将其应用于实际场景。同时，我也在团队合作中锻炼了自己的协作能力和沟通能力。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 0em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A25%3A48%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%871.png?Expires=2033274349&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=5E5wVN%2BdeNzfQVU%2B1bLN%2FStex1M%3D" width="829" height="454" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px; width: 829px; height: 454px;"/><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">三、收获与感悟</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">技能与能力的提升：通过项目实践，我巩固了专业知识，提升了编程能力和项目管理能力，为未来的职业发展奠定了坚实基础。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A26%3A58%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png?Expires=2033274419&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=crmQjV%2BvrNvCrUVG7J6kZfVU1po%3D" width="827" height="573" style="width: 827px; height: 573px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">自我认知的深化：在项目中，我认识到自己的优点和不足，明确了未来需要努力的方向，也增强了自己的自信心。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A27%3A43%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png?Expires=2033274464&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=4eSE24%2FxwHmNATJo8%2FqOG%2FwlFz0%3D"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A28%3A01%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%874.png?Expires=2033274482&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=rAKk9NPkmI57ODHayA4pw9nBCYw%3D" width="824" height="625" style="width: 824px; height: 625px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A28%3A17%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%875.png?Expires=2033274498&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=VsYF7W5cv9WYWV%2FjuqBQkgcwGgU%3D"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai; font-size: 16px;">团队合作的重要性：在项目中，我深刻体会到团队合作的力量。与团队成员共同协作、共同解决问题，让我更加珍视团队的力量和合作的精神。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 19px"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/blockchain/img/2024-06-09%2014%3A28%3A36%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%876.png?Expires=2033274516&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=iCn25Dbw65wD43yEzL%2FysmFfmGE%3D" width="819" height="549" style="width: 819px; height: 549px;"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">四、参加实训项目的建议</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; text-indent: 37px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 楷体, 楷体_GB2312, SimKai;">积极寻找实践机会：不要满足于书本知识，要勇于尝试和实践，将所学知识应用到实际项目中。</span></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; font-size: 22px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-align: left; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></h2>